The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                         3                                                                                      Good Morning
      Hello It's Sunday , August 29 , 2010                
	Quiz    Drop in at the Mother Teresa Quiz by Derek OBrien at Don Bosco Park Circus, 10am.        
	Film festival    Enjoy films on Mother Teresa at the Third Mother Teresa International Film Festival 2010 at Nandan, 1pm onwards.        
	Drape show    Check out the sari exhibition-cum-sale by Indian Silk House, College Street Market, at Ice Skating Rink, 10.30am to 7.30pm.        
	Seminar    Attend a seminar on Comprehensive Trauma Care Management at ICCR, 11am.        
	Music    Enjoy a solo performance of Tagore songs by Alok Roy Chowdhury at Sisir Mancha, 10.30am.				   Move on to an evening of Tagores songs, dance and plays organised by Biswabhara Pran at GD Birla Sabhagar, 6pm.                                                                                                                                               
